data.description: CALL NOW to find out about the 100.00 Down Payment FHA Loan, yes that's right 100.00 Down Payment. This Blue Springs beauty boasts both a fabulous location AND fantastic price! Offering 3 bedrooms & two full baths, this spacious split entry home also features maintenance free siding. Country kitchen features hardwood floors, ample cabinetry, and double pantry-- so lots of storage space! The options abound! FANTASTIC backyard with newer, oversized deck & built in hot tub -- perfect for entertaining! Plus-- lots of privacy! Large lot backs to greenspace-- park like setting with mature trees and lovely landscaping. Another big bonus-- large shed perfect for storing your toys and lawn tools! This property is ready for you to call home! Quick access to I-70 makes for an easy commute-- PLUS, close to great shopping & restaurants. Award winning Blue Springs Schools! This one won't last long! This is a HUD acquired home sold as is Case# 291-603172
